    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still logging in. everything just feels... heavy. the lab results came back today and it's over. the funding is gone, the advisor isn't even returning my emails, and i realized i have absolutely nothing else. no hobbies, no friends, just this. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for a life that doesn't even want me back.",
