    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"ashes\" thing sounds a lot more exhausting than actually being done. starting over sounds like just another mountain to climb that i don't have the strength for. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to stop feeling this constant, heavy pull to keep performing, keep trying, keep being... something. i just want peace.",
